snippet.title: Secret Trouble Gameplay (PC Game)
snippet.description:
A totally ordinary, average wizard is having problems with some troublesome magical artifacts. One of those troublesome magical beings is you. Try and juggle as much as you can and earn as much points as you can.
Support the developer by purchasing the game on steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1688440/Secret_Trouble/
